       &kp LALT        &kp LGUI      &kp LCTRL       &kp LSHFT        &mkp MB2    &mkp MB5  &kp LEFT        &kp DOWN        &kp UP        &kp RIGHT
&none  &none           &none         &kp DEL         &kp ESC          &kp TAB     &mkp MB4  &kp HOME        &kp PAGE_DOWN   &kp PAGE_UP   &kp END          &none
                                     &kp ENTER       &kp SPACE        &kp BSPC    &kp BSPC  &kp SPACE       &kp ENTER
            >;
